### cookbooks

### get all cookbooks
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cookbooks

### add cookbook
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cookbooks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Flavor",
  "authors": [
    "Yotam Ottolenghi", 
    "Ixta Belfrage"
  ],
  "isbn10": "3831040869",
  "isbn13": "9783831484100"
}

### edit cookbook (replace :id with actual cookbook ID)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/cookbooks/:id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Flavor: More than 100 Simple Recipes for a More Complex World",
  "authors": [
    "Yotam Ottolenghi", 
    "Ixta Belfrage"
  ]
}

### remove cookbook (replace :id with actual cookbook ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/cookbooks/:id

### identify cookbook from back cover image
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cookbooks/identification
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
